            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='14'>FEATURE INSIGHTS</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>• Early Blight produces the largest lesion footprints among all classes.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>• Late Blight shows the most centralized detection distribution.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>• Healthy plants maintain the highest shape consistency.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>• Larger lesions generally correspond to longer lesion boundaries.</run>
            <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>• Geometric features provide clear separation between disease categories.</run>
